<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dully" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dully,</orth> sluggishly, tediously: <cit><quote>the beast that bears me plods d. on,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 50.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 50, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. sluggardized at home,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. I, 1, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the time shall not go d. by us,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.379" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 379</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>